{"tid":35721,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳 業 坤 晒「 全 裸 照 」嚇 壞 網 友","createTime":"2016-12-12T09:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T12:18:32.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"523d52dd8e53674adacaa9cc52949279d10fb312","tid":35721,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:20:54.000Z","msg":"歌手吳業坤（坤坤）今年初出席頒奬典禮，因為着住條褲太緊令「小坤坤」激凸，成為一時佳話，估唔到坤坤最近大突破，豁出去玩「野外露出」，咁大膽！！！<br />\n<br />\n實情係坤坤呢日喺社交網晒出影CD COVER嘅花絮照，仲將自己個BODY打格，啲格仔透現肉色，睇落激似全裸，好難唔令人亂諗囉！網友睇見張相，都忍唔住大叫：「該煨！」有人仲勸坤坤着返條褲㖭，認真搞笑！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20161212/photo/bkn-20161212080232315-1212_00862_001_02b.jpg?20161212084804\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20161212%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161212080232315-1212_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20161212084804&h=18e71d68&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"019770a8318f1dcce613a038fe84218fa93bd2da","tid":35721,"uid":10726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:21:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac74968bf631806c2cda0f05686344f6b71405c","tid":35721,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好柒啊屌"},{"pid":"bf7f565ed9a6029ef0363504b88ef50434320d80","tid":35721,"uid":12782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12d56ab01376b3471d0d2e1c65a3beac50dceac","tid":35721,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:23:05.000Z","msg":"我叫一二三四"},{"pid":"07b19064b74e1227961f305dac2b951cd65a5974","tid":35721,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:37:34.000Z","msg":"佢真係好識做新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo